{"msg":{"practice":[{"id":131,"question":"在公司内部分享会上，某个高管分享了自己多年的工作经验，并总结出了一系列规则和道理。<br/><br/>你觉得可信度如何？","type":1,"analysis":"个人经历容易以偏概全是这种证据的一个特征，但并不是说就一定以偏概全呀。工作中很多问题还是需要用经验解决的，经验是高管个人价值的一部分，不要学了批判性思维就把一切都否定哦","pic":null,"difficulty":3,"knowledgeId":11,"sceneId":1,"del":false,"problemId":12,"sequence":1,"example":false,"practiceUid":"TT012B004B001X01001","score":50,"choiceList":[{"id":391,"questionId":131,"subject":"可信度很高，工作那么多年，能做到那个位子，应该还是很靠谱的","sequence":1,"isRight":true,"selected":false},{"id":392,"questionId":131,"subject":"不可信，这是“个人经历”类型的证据，容易以偏概全","sequence":2,"isRight":false,"selected":false}],"discussList":[{"id":2077,"warmupPracticeId":131,"repliedId":null,"comment":"没学批判性思维前，遇到这种情况会觉得可信。学了之后就觉得要具体事情具体分析，客观性的道理可信度高，如果是主观上的道理受个人经历背景等局限可信度不那么高。中庸一点应该说可信度较高。","openid":null,"addTime":1492420134000,"priority":0,"repliedOpenid":null,"repliedComment":null,"del":0,"repliedName":null,"name":"锦慕兰","avatar":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/ib7IQ03GF98XpSLeBeWNiaS3skBBT8HsSPCyTJe0kT5cTVYOdIHeuEGdvfS3eHvDbZuYZcRIMxiaz0lVQjiadx2BdTtgw0bzCCn0/0","discussTime":"2017-04-17"},{"id":1985,"warmupPracticeId":131,"repliedId":null,"comment":"B项说“容易以偏概全”，但又没说是“一定会”，为什么不对呢?","openid":null,"addTime":1491992313000,"priority":0,"repliedOpenid":null,"repliedComment":null,"del":0,"repliedName":null,"name":"奥薇朵","avatar":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/ib7IQ03GF98VsBltdAuYibP8qXABtDx0IJKTl2RJuKDTUNf3icV39jpZK0CW27iaLAbwibNJF6RibOGsR6IFaLabOv9JgT9BKbkkaR/0","discussTime":"2017-04-12"},{"id":1694,"warmupPracticeId":131,"repliedId":null,"comment":"进坑\uD83D\uDE02","openid":null,"addTime":1491143020000,"priority":0,"repliedOpenid":null,"repliedComment":null,"del":0,"repliedName":null,"name":"王佳","avatar":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/siaKjia9aBPcJHOCEV6z4AywoaJCYTv4hicL3wib7fApyhLPNJiaroIhefibZ5St8K9AWkmRhDQ3astuE22Q5cDMLXKe5anwROuryia/0","discussTime":"2017-04-02"},{"id":1480,"warmupPracticeId":131,"repliedId":1439,"comment":"你说的误导性具体是指什么呢","openid":null,"addTime":1490694077000,"priority":0,"repliedOpen